      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOW HIGH (2) is a progressive type who recorded his 3rd career win last time out (25.75) at this track. Is yet to taste defeat at this course. Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Hard to fault his form and he makes plenty of appeal. TEMORA TERROR (1) produced a modest effort most recently when fifth at Wagga over 525m behind Mob Mentality (31.60) in a Grade 5. Placed at his previous run. Form from his last run is proving strong. Expected to feature in the finish. JET BLACK COLD (3) was strongly fancied last time but finished third (26.07), beaten 0.8 lengths. Won at his only start from this box. Nicely placed to grab a well-deserved win. SECRET JOKER (4) looks a top-three hope after a break.",
